    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolute showroom condition! I\u2019ve totally babied this car from day one, and it still feels and smells like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage and looks stunning from every angle. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection! It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a collector-grade Shelby GT350, featuring the high-revving 5.2L 'Voodoo' V8 engine equipped with a flat-plane crankshaft for an 8,250 RPM redline. This specimen utilizes a Tremec TR-3160 six-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential with a 3.73 final drive. The chassis dynamics are managed by the MagneRide Damping System, providing active hydraulic adjustments to counter lateral G-forces. Stopping power is delivered by six-piston front Brembo calipers over two-piece cross-drilled rotors. This vehicle is in impeccable mechanical condition, retaining its factory-spec tolerances, original aero-splitters, and a pristine undercarriage. No aftermarket modifications have been performed, preserving the integrity of the Ford Performance engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Luxury Sedan. Mint condition. Garage kept. Single owner. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Detailed service records provided.",
      "price": 42500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
