    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. Meticulously garage-kept and hand-washed, the exterior retains its deep, original factory luster without a single stone chip or swirl mark. Step inside to an interior that still carries that new-car aroma; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any bolster wear, and every digital interface remains crisp and fully operational. Mechanically, it is flawless, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance and strictly low-mileage weekend use. Included are all original manuals, two master keys, and a clean title. This isn't just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
