      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the dealership for the first time! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garaged and spotless, so it\u2019s running perfectly and looks stunning. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
